SUMMARY:Bit Gen Gamer Fest XIX
DESCRIPTION:Bit Gen Gamer Fest powers up once more as planet Earth’s largest one-day video game music festival. Bit Gen 19 storms the legendary Ottobar in Baltimore\, Maryland\, for an all-day\, all-out celebration of the music and madness that defined a generation. And it all goes down this Saturday\, August 23rd! \nThis year’s lineup showcases some of the most iconic and electrifying performers in the video game music scene\, spanning nearly 30 years of pixel-fueled history. With two stages running on a ping-pong-style alternating schedule\, the action never stops. Fuel your combo meter with video game-inspired cocktails\, dive into a curated selection of free-play arcade and console games\, and let your nostalgia pacman feast until it bursts with joy. \nThis is raw\, unfiltered nerd culture turned all the way up. No panels. No cosplay contests (or should we?). Just pure\, live\, VGM performed by the best in the game. Bit Gen Gamer Fest continues to cement its legacy as the galaxy’s most relentless celebration of video game music and the weird\, wonderful people who love it. We hope to see you at the Ottobar this weekend!
URL:https://baltimoreindiegames.com/event/bit-gen-gamer-fest-xix/
END:VEVENT
