SUMMARY:Ludum Dare 58
DESCRIPTION:Ludum Dare is an online event where games are made from scratch in a weekend. \nBIG is planning to host an in-person site for people who want to get together in person to make games. Location details will be announced in early September. \nldjam.com | Ludum Dare game jam
